Утверждение
I/We/You/They + V
He/She/it + V +s(es)

Отрицание
I/We/You/They + do not(don't) + V
He/She/It + does not(doesn't) + V

Вопрос
Do + I/We/You/They + V
Does + He/She/It + V

Вопрос(специальный)
QW + Do + I/We/You/They + V
QW + Does + He/She/It + V

I work - he works

Вопрос
Am + I
Are + we/you/they
Is + she/he/it
